    "en": {
      "title": "International Monetary Fund's news about Sri Lanka!",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The International Monetary Fund is in constant contact with the Sri Lankan authorities, said its spokesperson, Kerry Rice.",
        "Spokesperson of the International Monetary Fund, Kerry Rice, who has said that they intend to start negotiations with high-level officials, has also said that adequate guarantees on debt sustainability are necessary for any new loan program."
